HP is above a certain value."

"PP Convert/Ring
Temporarily increases PP Auto-recovery
while decreasing max HP."

"Elemental PP Restore Field/Ring
Creates a field that boosts PP regen when you
attack matching the elemental weakness."

"Boost Slayer
Increases damage towards boosted
enemies, and decreases damage from them."

"Just Guard Sonic Arrow
Sonic Arrow activates after a Just Guard
when using Sword-type weapons."

"Just Guard Heavenly Fall
Heavenly Fall activates after a Just Guard
when using Wired Lance-type weapons."

"Just Guard Rising Flag
Rising Flag activates after a Just Guard
when using Partizan-type weapons."

"Double Saber Kamaitachi
Specific PAs activate Kamaitachi
without consuming Double Saber Gear."

"Twin Dagger Air Chase
Normal attacks and certain PAs in
the air will chase a locked on target."

"Knuckle Chase
Normal attacks and certain PAs on the
ground will chase locked-on enemies."

"Front Stylish Roll
Allows Twin Machineguns to perform
a Stylish Roll forwards."

"Katana Gear Guard Release
Hold Guard to force a Gear release.
Gear gain is increased each grind level."

"Dual Blade Snatch
Inflicts striking damage to enemies while
moving using the Dual Blade weapon action."

"Tech Charge Parry
While using a teching weapon, you can
Just Guard by starting to charge a Technique."

"Recast Reverser Field
Reduces recast time of Reverser Field."

"Hunter Gear Save
While Hunter Gear Boost is in effect, decreases
the rate that Gear empties and is consumed."

"High Time Keep
Increases the amount of damage needed to
cancel out High Time."

"Short Combat
When using Katana Combat,
basic attacks no longer track enemies."

"Wide Area Heal
Increases the range of
the A.I.S. skill \"Area Heal\"."

"Quick Blaster
The A.I.S. skill \"Photon Blaster\" activates faster,
but its turning speed is reduced."

"Early Rise
Reduces the time that an A.I.S.
must wait to be resurrected."

"Light Armor
Reduces the PP cost of the A.I.S. Boost,
but increases damage taken."

"Burn Guard
Gives resistance to the \"Burn\" status effect."

"Freeze Guard
Gives resistance to the \"Freeze\" status effect."

"Shock Guard
Gives resistance to the \"Shock\" status effect."

"Mirage Guard
Gives resistance to the \"Mirage\" status effect."

"Poison Guard
Gives resistance to the \"Poison\" status effect."

"Panic Guard
Gives resistance to the \"Panic\" status effect."

"Bullet Bow Homing
Adds a homing ability to a
Bullet Bow's charged normal attack."

"Jet Boots Elemental Keep
Element is kept upon performing a weapon
action. Elemental Burst is no longer activated."

"Standing Sign
Display a visual effect when
in the \"stationary\" status."

"Another Launcher Mode
Changes the trajectory and boosts the
power of a Launcher's normal attack."

"Wand Element Change
When activating Wand Gear, change element
based on the last charged Tech used."

"Mate Lovers
Increases usage speed and healing amount
for Mate-type items."

"J Reversal Cover/Ring
Restores HP upon performing a
Just Reversal."

"Heal Share/Ring
Heals surrounding characters by a certain
amount upon recovering HP."

"Adrenaline/Ring
Increases duration of received
Shifta and Deband effects."

"JB Tech Arts Short Charge
Technique charge time is shortened
when following a Jet Boots PA."

"Slow Dive Roll
Increases the duration of Dive Roll
by reducing its speed."

"Launcher Non-Weak Bonus
While using Launchers, Weak Hit Advance
applies even if not hitting a weak point."

"Step Jump
Start running again by jumping
after a Step Action or Dive Roll."

"Just Reversal JA Combo
You can perform a Just Attack following
a Just Reversal."

"Air Reversal
Enables the use of Just Reversal
while still in the air."

"Wide Support/Ring
Increases the effect range of
Resta, Anti, Shifta and Deband."

"J Reversal PP Gain/Ring
Restores PP upon activating
Just Reversal."

"Healing Guard/Ring
Upon a successful Just Guard, restore HP
for yourself and all nearby characters."

"JA Bonus
Increases the damage of Just Attacks,
except for Techniques."

"Effort Symbol Hunter
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Ranger
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Force
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Fighter
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Gunner
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Techer
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Braver
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Bouncer
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Summoner
A badge signifying experience as a strong
soldier, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Effort Symbol Hero
A badge signifying experience as a valiant
hero, earned by facing significant hardship."

"Friends' Protection
Ring of friendship for Itsuki and RINA.
Reduces damage."

"Tech Arts JA PP Save/Ring
Reduces PP costs when performing
consecutive Just Attacks of PAs/Techniques."

"Jumping Dodge
When used from the subpalette, uses
a high jump to avoid enemy attacks."

"Near Auto Target
Pet will attack the nearest enemy to the
player with one wave of the takt."

"Photon Blade Homing
Adds a homing ability to Photon Blade
attacks."

"Slow Fighter Action
Extends the duration and reduces
the speed of Fighter weapon actions."

"Another Rod Shoot Mode
Rod Shoot's projectile explodes on impact,
affecting enemies within range."

"Just Reversal Blast
Inflicts damage to nearby enemies
upon landing from a Just Reversal"

"Mag Excite
Boosts the frequency and power of your
Mag's auto action. Excludes SP auto actions."

"Step Just Attack Combo
Creates a JA timing window when executing
Step."

"Quick Mate/Ring
Speeds up usage of Mate-type items."

"Critical Field/Ring
Generates a field around yourself
that increases critical hit rate."

"Point Weak Bullet
Weak Bullet will always hit a locked-on
target regardless of any obstructions."

"Katana Combat Count Up
Increases Katana Combat's hit count."

"Atomizer Lovers
Allows quick usage of Atomizer-type items
as well as increases their recovery effect."

"Flame Tech S-Charge/Ring
Reduces the charge time of fire techniques."

"HP Restorate/Ring
Gradually restores HP once your
HP falls below a particular threshold."

"Twin Machinegun Stance Up
Adds increased S-ATK and R-ATK to stance
skill effects when a Twin Machinegun is equipped."

"Party of Toughness
Reduces the damage received from enemies
if in a party of 2 players or more."

"Weak Hit PP Gain
Increase PP recovery amount when
attacking normal weak spots."
